data.chText: 微不足道的；不重要的；不值一提的
data.enText: of very little importance or size and not worth considering

simple_means.memory_skill: neg 否认，拒绝 + lig 选择 + ible 可…的 → 不用选择的 → 可以忽视的

tr: so small as to be meaningless

example: he considered the prize too paltry for the lives it must cost

value.def: An amount or effect that is negligible is so small that it is not worth considering or worrying about.

example.ex: The pay that the soldiers received was negligible...
example.tran: 士兵拿到的军饷少得可怜。

example.ex: Senior managers are convinced that the strike will have a negligible impact.
example.tran: 高层主管们相信罢工的影响微不足道。

value.tran: 微不足道的;可忽略不计的

rootsaffixes.indicate: = to deny 否认, 拒绝
rootsaffixes.title: neg
